<content>
    <para id="id8592422">The chemistry of the alkali metals is dominated by the stability of the +1 oxidation state and the noble gas configuration of the M<sup>+</sup> cation. The alkali metals all have low first ionization energies (<link target-id="id1172521238986"/>) but very high second ionization energies. </para>
